vista.set
Class DataReferenceMath

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.DataReferenceMath

public class DataReferenceMath
extends java.lang.Object

This class defines the math operations on data references. These math operations are proxies which are performed only as needed.

Version:
$Id: DataReferenceMath.java,v 1.1 2003/10/02 20:49:20 redwood Exp $
